{"tid":929322,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[初試輪回] 你的選擇是...?","createTime":"2018-12-05T13:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T03:25:11.000Z","uid":221903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f1156fe24331dd12d2e532768120c0ac51a28c","tid":929322,"uid":221903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"新手試筆，請輕插。選項會以最多票數形式投出，只計正評，不計負評。<br />\n試下水溫先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n「發生什麼事了？」當我醒來後發現周圍是一片漆黑，黑得伸手不見五指。<br />\n<br />\n我不是上一秒還在家中開心打機中，下一秒怎麼出現在這裡。<br />\n<br />\n「是我打機出現了幻覺嗎？」我默默的念著。<br />\n<br />\n我查看了身體一下，發現左手上多了一隻高科技手錶，手錶上顯示著一個時間：<br />\n「３０：００」<br />\n<br />\n「這是哪裡?」一位女士的聲音從我前方傳出，語氣中能聽出她有點驚惶失措。難道這並不是我的幻覺，是真實？<br />\n<br />\n好了，下一步應該做些什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\nA 調查手錶<br />\nB 與女士對話<br />\nC 調查周圍環境"},{"pid":"a1c5f56c6641939d1687d9cf3dbea65c0a28aeee","tid":929322,"uid":221903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"A 調查手錶"},{"pid":"1365fca4de9e12763ff29d31ddb48ad5b40f10d0","tid":929322,"uid":221903,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"B 與女士對話"},{"pid":"751493d6d5cacabd7b902e6df5787875e481f345","tid":929322,"uid":221903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"C 調查周圍環境"},{"pid":"e1904d9d88e2baca5ad51317e09603c0ef3765e9","tid":929322,"uid":221903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推一下"},{"pid":"3ed1d301dd9be457310591c61179b96376935594","tid":929322,"uid":41992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"B<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ae28b4f970db529dc1fec1df86cb5328b43cd6","t